latestPosts.caption:
My second Met Gala with @teyanataylor 💙

It is truly a gift to get to work with a person that I can now get to call a friend . Not only is this your second met gala but it’s mine too and we both experienced it together. This will forever be marked in our lives and the more Mets to come 💫 

Now you know I’m dropping all the makeup heat 🔥

PRODUCT LIST 💎 

EYES - on her brows I used  @maccosmetics eyebrow styler “spiked” . As shadows @hudabeauty “blue and green color block obsessions” . I also used @natashadenona “Bronze eyeshadow Palette” & @juviasplace “warrior III”. On her waterline I used @urbandecaycosmetics glide on liner “chaos”. Lashes were (eyelash extensions) 

FACE - to prep her face @charlottetilbury “magic cream” along with @westmanatelier “Peau de soleil” Creme bronze highlighter all over her face . To create a more glowy canvas I also used @supergoop “glow screen” sunscreen . 

FOUNDATION + CONCEALER - @givenchybeauty Prisme libre skin-caring Matte foundation. To conceal @tartecosmetics shape tape Concealer . 

CONTOUR + SET : @hudabeautyshop @hudabeauty foundation stick “cocoa bean + nutmeg”. To set under eyes and set face , @hudabeauty powder “banana bread” x “Kunafa” . To set face @charlottetilbury flawless finish foundation powder “3 & 4” . 

BRONZER + BLUSH: @guccibeauty “Gucci Poudre De Beauté Éclat Soleil Powder” shade 4 & 5”. @rarebeauty cream Matte blush “ terracota” . 

HIGHLIGHT : @westmanatelier on top of cheek to act as intensifier for @fentybeauty diamond bomb all over veil “pure copper sparkle . Also applied on top @patmcgrathreal x Bridgerton skintillating diamond body shimmer powder .  To set her face I used @milkmakeup hydrogrip setting spray + @urbandecaycosmetics all nighter . 

LIPS : @makeupforever “608” x “612”. @fentybeauty “honey waffles “ + “universal rose nude” lastly topped with @patmcgrathreal “Aliengelic”. 
 
#teyanataylor #metgala #metgala2022 #explore #feed #fyp #yeikaglow

Hair & makeup by @yeikaglow & @curt_cobain 

Nails : @chuenails 🤍

Thank you God 🤍🤍🤍🤍

Did y’all watch Straw on Netflix yet?! 🎬 

This was the very first movie I ever worked on , and all I can say is, thank you God. 🙏🏽

Endless gratitude to my muse @teyanataylor for believing in me and letting me be part of your journey. Thank you for the opportunity to meet the one and only @tylerperry.

We keep creating memories, and I’m truly honored to be part of your story just like you’re part of mine.
So proud of your performance in this film… and proud of myself too, for making sure you look stunning in every scene, every moment, and every carpet.

🌹 The rose keeps growing. God keeps showing out.
#Straw #Netflix #Grateful #MakeupByMe
